<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.2.8">
<l>iruma laipō letirnta malla riruva raṅka mericey tāyuṉ</l>
<l>tiruma lintu tikaḻu mārvu tēkka vanteṉ ṉalku lēṟi</l>
<l>yorumu laiyai vāyma ṭutto rumu laiyai neruṭik koṇṭu</l>
<l>virumu laiyum muṟaimu ṟaiyā yēṅki yēṅki yiruntu ṇāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You made the limbs burn of the two wrestlers,</l>
<l rend="indent">like huge mountains, who opposed [you].</l>
<l>Come, climb onto my hips to drink to fill up to [your] beautiful,</l>
<l>sacred, shining chest, suckling one breast with [your] mouth,</l>
<l>and taking and rubbing the other with [your] hands,</l>
<l>each breast in turn, crying over and over, sit [and] drink!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
